FBIS4-8840 "dreeu075_c_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-075 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 CZECH REPUBLIC Pensioner's Movement Becomes Political Party Pensioner's Movement Becomes Political Party AU1804202594 Prague CESKY DENIK in Czech 12 Apr 94 p 2 AU1804202594 Prague CESKY DENIK Czech BFN [Article by "(jis)": "The Establishment of a New Party"] [Text] Kolin--At its extraordinary nationwide assembly, the Movement of Retired People for Social Security decided to transform itself into a political party--Pensioners for Social Securities. This change will not reportedly have any impact on the political line and the party's decision to fight on behalf of socially endangered individuals among our people. The main stress will be laid on the existential interests of the pensioners. According to Otakar Skalsky, press spokesman of the party, thousands of new members have joined the party recently.
